descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://s25.postimg.org/6n2pc47vz/Screen_Shot182.jpg[/img][/center][center]i'm indonesian and sorry for my bad english.
this is my fist mod ever. :D

- Indonesian School Uniform -
I wish this mod isnt too sexy for school uniform XD

- How To Get -
1. you can get by console. just type "Indonesian" and it will be shown up by 3 part
armor, skirt and tie
2. Or  you can craft them in forge, in leather section.

- Issues -
1. There some cliping part during extreme animation.
2. Small annoying glowing part in a back, i feel isn't not a big problem. :P
3. Weight Slider Curently Didn't Support :P

- Note -
Only Contains 3 Part.
armor, skirt and tie no additional item, etc

I Hope U Enjoy This Freakin Mod :D
i'm realy appreciate for feedback or critism.

and Thanks for feedback, i hope this will be part of learning
and be better for future mods :D
